00:40:18,460 --> 00:40:19,380
Did something happen

928
00:40:19,380 --> 00:40:20,460
when you were young?

929
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:21,520
Or have any trauma?

930
00:40:22,730 --> 00:40:23,610
I just think

931
00:40:24,510 --> 00:40:25,390
when I'm alone,

932
00:40:25,420 --> 00:40:26,220
