934
00:40:30,220 --> 00:40:31,730
That sounds nice.

935
00:40:32,020 --> 00:40:34,420
But I think you just don't have any friends.

936
00:40:37,700 --> 00:40:39,060
Do you want to die?

937
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:42,380
I was

938
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:43,600
