981
00:42:15,580 --> 00:42:16,300
In the end,

982
00:42:16,870 --> 00:42:18,260
you took Liu Fu's gold

983
00:42:18,300 --> 00:42:19,460
behind my back.

984
00:42:20,270 --> 00:42:21,110
You're just

985
